added.has_closer_water_fog: • These biomes have a shorter view distance underwater.
added.has_structure/ancient_city: • Ancient city can generate in these biomes.
added.plays_underwater_music: • The player hears the special underwater music when underwater in these biomes.
added.produces_corals_from_bonemeal: • Coral can be farmed by using bone meal in these biomes.
added.required_ocean_monument_surrounding: • These biomes must be present around a location where a monument is possible to generate.
added.water_on_map_outlines: • These biomes appear as water on map outlines.
